## Project file layout

```
.
├── CMakeLists.txt
├── macros/
│   └── tracker_vis.mac              Geant4 visualisation macro
├── exec/
│   └── main_g4.cpp                  Entry point, CLI parsing
├── include/
│   ├── MaterialManager.h            Material definitions
│   ├── TrackerPlaneBuilder.h        Geometry builder interface
│   ├── TrackerDetectorConstruction.hh
│   ├── TrackerHit.hh                TubeHit and TileHit classes
│   ├── TrackerSD.hh                 Sensitive detector
│   ├── TrackerRunAction.hh          ROOT file + TTree ownership
│   ├── TrackerEventAction.hh        Per-event hit collection and Fill()
│   └── TrackerPrimaryGeneratorAction.hh
└── src/
    ├── MaterialManager.cpp
    ├── TrackerPlaneBuilder.cpp      Full detector geometry
    ├── TrackerDetectorConstruction.cc
    ├── TrackerSD.cc
    ├── TrackerRunAction.cc
    ├── TrackerEventAction.cc
    └── TrackerPrimaryGeneratorAction.cc
```
